name: Efemerides
body:
### Efemerides.
Efemerides is an easy component for Joomla to manage important historical events. 

Support Joomla 1.5, 1.6 and working in progress to support Joomla 2.5.
tagline: Efemerides is an easy component for Joomla to manage important historical events
